這部電影主要獲得了褒貶不一的評價，但比起前部還要進步許多。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]基於70評論得分55％<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_purge_anarchy_2014/ | title = ''The Purge: Anarchy'' | publisher = ''[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]'' | date = 2014-07-17 | accessdate = 2014-07-17 | archive-date = 2019-07-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190713052929/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_purge_anarchy_2014/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]網站上，基於18位評論家，得分49/100，表示「混合或平均的評價」<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-purge-anarchy | title=''The Purge: Anarchy'' | publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] | accessdate=2014-07-17 | archive-date=2019-05-06 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190506194635/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-purge-anarchy | dead-url=no }}</ref>。在[[CinemaScore|CinemaScore]]上則獲得「B」的評價，比起前部的「C」要好上一些<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://edition.cnn.com/2014/07/21/showbiz/movies/box-office-report-planet-of-the-apes-purge-anarchy/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-08-08 |archive-date=2014-08-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140810193521/http://edition.cnn.com/2014/07/21/showbiz/movies/box-office-report-planet-of-the-apes-purge-anarchy/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 票房 ===
該片在北美的3,303劇院上映<ref>{{cite web | url = http://m.hollywoodreporter.com/entry/view/id/390520 | title = Box-Office Previews: 'Purge,' 'Planes' Sequels Face Off Against 'Dawn of the Planet of the Apes' | author = Rebecca Ford | publisher = ''[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]'' | date = 2014-07-17 | accessdate = 2014-07-17 | archive-date = 2014-07-27 | archive-url = https://archive.today/20140727053228/http://m.hollywoodreporter.com/entry/view/id/390520 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。並於第一晚上就賺進了260萬美元<ref>{{cite news|last1=Lang|first1=Brent|title=‘Sex Tape’ Attracts $1.1 Mil, ‘Purge: Anarchy’ Scares Up $2.6 Mil at Thursday Box Office|url=http://variety.com/2014/film/news/sex-tape-attracts-1-1-mil-purge-anarchy-scares-up-2-6-mil-at-thursday-box-office-1201264492/|accessdate=2014-07-18|publisher=variety.com|date=2014-07-18|archive-date=2014-07-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140718182145/http://variety.com/2014/film/news/sex-tape-attracts-1-1-mil-purge-anarchy-scares-up-2-6-mil-at-thursday-box-office-1201264492/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在它的首場週末，該片票房收入達到2840萬美元，名列第二位。票房總計8226萬2000美元。

== 續集 ==
{{main|國定殺戮日：大選之年}}
2014年8月，傑森·布倫表示，第三部作品正在計畫中。據布倫透露，第三部電影主要敘述革命和首次殺戮日。電影定於2015年的夏天釋出<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.tv3.ie/entertainment_article.php?locID=1.803.810&article=143142 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-09-02 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140903090400/http://www.tv3.ie/entertainment_article.php?locID=1.803.810&article=143142 |archivedate=2014-09-03 }}</ref>。2014年10月6日證實，第三部電影確定推出，而狄莫納哥也將回歸編劇和執導<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2014/10/the-purge-sequel-james-demonaco-blumhouse-846718/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-11-11 |archive-date=2018-06-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180620015409/https://deadline.com/2014/10/the-purge-sequel-james-demonaco-blumhouse-846718/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。第三部作品定於2016年7月1日上映。2015年7月，葛里洛將回歸演出第三集<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://bloody-disgusting.com/news/3355767/frank-grillo-returning-third-the-purge/ |title=Frank Grillo Returning For Another ‘Purge’! |accessdate=2015-08-05 |archive-date=2015-08-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150806130410/http://bloody-disgusting.com/news/3355767/frank-grillo-returning-third-the-purge/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

